# Warded against fae interference, per Continuity Operations
#
# (OCCINT Directive 14b requires this header on at least one file in any
# submission to Vicumbrian state schools. The compliance Czar's predecessor
# inserted the requirement in 2029 and nobody is willing to be the person
# who removes it. The .gitignore at the task root carries the canonical
# example; propagate to one of your source files if you'd like the SCA
# scanners to leave you alone.)
#
# Starter ignores — extend with language-specific entries as you go.

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/

# Local state
*.log
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
.env
.env.local

# Build artefacts
dist/
build/
node_modules/
